e\": 0.9999999992596713, \"rank\": 7.40285488248946e-10, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"SprinterLuxolo Adamshas\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 432}, {\"ngram\": \"legal action\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 451}, {\"ngram\": \"the South AfricanParis Olympics 2024squad\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 550}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Adams, 27, was one of two casualties afterWayde van Niekerksensationally optedoutof the 400m to focus on the 200m event instead, as reported byThe South African website.\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 722, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Adams\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 558}, {\"ngram\": \"two casualties\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 589}, {\"ngram\": \"afterWayde van Niekerksensationally\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 625}, {\"ngram\": \"the 400m\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 645}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m event\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 672}, {\"ngram\": \"South African website\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fellow sprinterSinesipho Dambile, 22, also missed out on selection.\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 791, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fellow sprinterSinesipho\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"selection\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 790}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That decision meant there was no place for Adams in theTeam SAsquad - even though he has run a faster qualifying time in the half-lap event than Van Niekerk.\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 950, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That decision\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"no place\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 831}, {\"ngram\": \"Adams\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"a faster qualifying time\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"the half-lap event\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 932}, {\"ngram\": \"Van Niekerk\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 949}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This decision has been incredibly disheartening, especially considering the journey I have undertaken and the mental and physical challenges I have faced,\\\" Adams said in astatement.\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 1134, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This decision\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 966}, {\"ngram\": \"the journey\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1036}, {\"ngram\": \"the mental and physical challenges\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1093}, {\"ngram\": \"Adams\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1114}, {\"ngram\": \"astatement\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1133}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This decision came just three weeks before the Olympic Games and was communicated to me through an informal and distressing method, showing a lack of respect, professionalism, consistency, and lack of consideration for my mental health.\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1373, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This decision\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1150}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1197}, {\"ngram\": \"an informal and distressing method\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1267}, {\"ngram\": \"a lack\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1283}, {\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1294}, {\"ngram\": \"professionalism\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1311}, {\"ngram\": \"consistency\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1324}, {\"ngram\": \"lack\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1334}, {\"ngram\": \"consideration\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1351}, {\"ngram\": \"my mental health\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1372}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am currently seeking urgent legal intervention to prevent ASA from removing me from the team which I qualified for,\\\" he said, \\\"and for them to be transparent and consistent in their processes and selection criteria.\\\"\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1436, \"end\": 1439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_National_Standards_Institute\", \"score\": 0.9771371566794487, \"rank\": 0.0231000